e> </gramGrp> peccati: <foreign xml:lang="gez">አበስኩ፡ ዐቢየ፡ ጌጋየ፡</foreign> <ref cRef="Job" loc="31,33">Job 31,33</ref>; <foreign xml:lang="gez">ሰማርያ፡ መንፈቀ፡ ኀጢአትከ፡ ኢአበሰት፡</foreign> <ref cRef="Hez." loc="16,51">Hez. 16,51</ref>; <lbl expand="cum">c.</lbl> <foreign xml:lang="gez">በ፡</foreign> instrumenti: <foreign xml:lang="gez">ኢተአብስ፡ በቃልከ፡</foreign> <ref cRef="Sir." loc="35,12">Sir. 35,12</ref>; <foreign xml:lang="gez">እመ፡ አበስነ፡ እመሂ፡ በቃል፡ አው፡ በምግባር፡ ወእመሂ፡ በኅሊና፡ ኅድግ፡</foreign> <ref cRef="Genz." loc="95">Genz. f. 95</ref>; <lbl expand="cum">c.</lbl> <foreign xml:lang="gez">ለ፡</foreign> ejus, in quem peccatur: <foreign xml:lang="gez">ኢተአብስ፡ ለሀገርከ፡</foreign> <ref cRef="Sir." loc="7,7">Sir. 7,7</ref>; <foreign xml:lang="gez">ዘአበሰ፡ ኢተ፡ አበሰ፡</foreign> <ref cRef="Jes." loc="21,2">Jes. 21,2</ref>; <ref cRef="Jes." loc="42,24">Jes. 42,24</ref>; <ref cRef="Jer." loc="8,14">Jer. 8,14</ref>; <ref cRef="Jer." loc="47,3">Jer. 47,3</ref>; <ref cRef="Dan." loc="9,8">Dan. 9,8</ref>; <ref cRef="Gen." loc="40,1">Gen. 40,1</ref>; <ref cRef="Ps." loc="50,5">Ps. 50,5</ref>; <ref cRef="Matth." loc="6,12">Matth. 6,12</ref>; vel <lbl expand="cum">c.</lbl> <foreign xml:lang="gez">ላዕለ፡</foreign> ejus rei vel personae, in qua peccatur: <ref cRef="Lev." loc="5,16">Lev. 5,16</ref>; <ref cRef="1 Reg." loc="19,4">1 Reg. 19,4</ref>; <ref cRef="Prov." loc="8,36">Prov. 8,36</ref>; <foreign xml:lang="gez">አበሱ፡ ላዕለ፡ ሕግየ፡</foreign> <ref cRef="Hos." loc="8,1">Hos. 8,1</ref>; <ref cRef="Esth." loc="1,16">Esth. 1,16</ref>; <foreign xml:lang="gez">ዘይገብር፡ ኀጢአተ፡ ይኤብስ፡ ላዕለ፡ ነፍሱ፡</foreign> <ref cRef="Sir." loc="19,4">Sir. 19,4</ref> (<foreign xml:lang="grc">πλημμελήσει</foreign>). <ref cRef="Sir." loc="10,29">Sir. 10,29</ref>; <ref cRef="1 Cor." loc="6,8">1 Cor. 6,8</ref>; vel <lbl expand="cum">c.</lbl> <foreign xml:lang="gez">ዲበ፡</foreign> <ref cRef="Act." loc="25,8">Act. 25,8</ref> Platt; vel <lbl expand="cum">c.</lbl> <foreign xml:lang="gez">በ፡</foreign>, ut: <ref cRef="Hen." loc="7,5">Hen. 7,5</ref>; <foreign xml:lang="gez">ዳዊት፡ አመ፡ ይኤብስ፡ በብእሲተ፡ ኦርዮ፡</foreign> <ref cRef="Did." loc="10">Did. 10</ref>; <ref cRef="Luc." loc="15,18">Luc. 15,18</ref>; <ref cRef="Luc." loc="15,21">Luc. 15,21</ref>; <ref cRef="1 Cor." loc="6,18">1 Cor. 6,18</ref>; <lbl expand="cum">c.</lbl> <foreign xml:lang="gez">ምስለ፡</foreign> <cit type="translation" xml:lang="la">
                            <quote> cum </quote>
                        </cit> aliquo: <foreign xml:lang="gez">መላእክት፡ አበሱ፡ ምስለ፡ አዋልደ፡ ሰብእ፡</foreign> <ref cRef="Kuf." loc="4">Kuf. 4</ref>; <lbl expand="cum">c.</lbl> <foreign xml:lang="gez">እምነ፡</foreign>, ut: <foreign xml:lang="gez">አበስከ፡ እመሐላ፡</foreign> (peccasti contra jusjurandum i.e. mutando j.) <ref cRef="Kuf." loc="37.">Kuf. 37.</ref> </sense>
               
